#: views/option-tabs/basic-tab.php:134
msgid "To use mobile caching with the Breeze plugin on Cloudways, you must enable the Device Detection feature through the Cloudways Platform. Please follow this <a href=\"%s\" target=\"_blank\">guide</a> to ensure the mobile cache functions properly."
