#: views/option-tabs/faq-tab.php:46
msgid ""
"Breeze is fully compatible with Aelia Currency Switcher Plugin. Also exclude the cookie of Aelia currency switcher plugin \"aelia_cs_selected_currency\" from Varnish settings.\n"
"<br/>\n"
"<br/>\n"
"If Varnish is active, you will need to exclude URLs and file type(s) in the Varnish configuration. If you are hosting WordPress websites on Cloudways servers, follow <a href=\"%s\" target=\"_blank\">this KB to exclude URLs from the Varnish cache</a>."
